{"tid":51321,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"翠林邨老街坊捱車撞 假牙飛出昏迷送院","createTime":"2016-12-23T06:31:36.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-23T07:56:03.000Z","uid":122,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3a3543531bdb03dfc3dfe49fd02fc873280547d7","tid":51321,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T06:31:36.000Z","msg":"將軍澳翠林邨欣林樓對開發生交通意外，早上9時19分，一輛運魚貨車沿翠琳路上斜，至欣林樓對開一名老婦由車頭左邊步出過馬路；61歲姓張司機收掣不及將她撞倒。86歲姓吳老婦頭及胸部受創，假牙甩脫飛出，昏迷不醒，由救護車送往伊利沙伯醫院搶救。<br />\n<br />\n警方事後封鎖現場調查，該處並非過路處，現場遺下假牙和波鞋。"},{"pid":"542be5730121c007c9d38a658efc2ac75b203bde","tid":51321,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T06:32:24.000Z","msg":"睇見都痛"},{"pid":"5a4464ba7f156b4dfcff80b3aafbb4ba783c6019","tid":51321,"uid":30800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T06:33:51.000Z","msg":"廢老又亂過馬路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d36a9c8634974bd9a75f1c3ac14149b5d9825172","tid":51321,"uid":37501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T06:33:56.000Z","msg":"廢老亂過馬路咁就害左司機成世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ee3894db7f1576a80692cd34c58ae8862cb8293","tid":51321,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T07:56:03.000Z","msg":"司機好慘"}]}